title: 294 - You With You
description:
Are you operating in Artificial Confidence? If you're not sure what that is, go back and watch episode 293! In this episode, the guys discuss ways to defeat artificial confidence. Artificial confidence gives control to whoever supplies it. When operating in artificial confidence, your goals will live or die based on the opinions of others. If you don't lose that thought process, you will always be at their mercy. Don't give others that type of control! Defeat artificial confidence.
